######################################
#  Solution

SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$BR $SPACE $BR 
$BBOLD  SOLUTION $EBOLD
$BR 
a) \( \displaystyle \lim_{x \to \infty} $a($b)^x = 0 \)
$BR $SPACE $BR
b) \( \displaystyle \lim_{t \to -\infty} $c($d)^t=0 \)
$BR $SPACE $BR
c) \( \displaystyle \lim_{t \to \infty} $m ($p $sign[$i] ($q)^t) = $m ($p $sign[$i] 0)= $ans_c \)
